@node Welcome

@{u}Welcome to the DoIcon documentation.@{uu}

@{b}Please read this documentation befor you use DoIcon, otherwise DoIcon
may modifies your icons in an unrecoverable way you did not intend!@{ub}

When reading this guide, please remember:
 @{i}All translation- and typing-errors are intentional 
 and belong to the whole work of art.@{ui} ;-))


DoIcon is only a small tool, but I hope you will like it,
if not... just delete it... ;-)


DoIcon was successfully tested on the following Amigas:

   · A3000 / 030 / OS 3.1
   · A4000 / 040 / OS 3.1
   · A2000 / 030 / OS 2.1
   · A2000 / 000 / OS 2.1
   · A500+ / 000 / OS 2.1
   · A600  / 000 / OS 2.1

@endnode

